一.WKInterfaceImage+download.m	NSURLSession ------> 未验证

在NSURLSessionTaskDelegate中的didReceiveChallenge，
canAuthenticateAgainstProtectionSpace方法进行证书验证

二.DetailViewController中的WKWebView支持https

在navigationDelegate的didReceiveAuthenticationChallenge方法中进行设置
- (void)webView:(WKWebView *)webView didReceiveAuthenticationChallenge:(NSURLAuthenticationChallenge *)challenge completionHandler:(void (^)(NSURLSessionAuthChallengeDisposition disposition, NSURLCredential * _Nullable credential))completionHandler{

    if ([challenge.protectionSpace.authenticationMethod isEqualToString:NSURLAuthenticationMethodServerTrust]) {

        NSURLCredential *card = [[NSURLCredential alloc]initWithTrust:challenge.protectionSpace.serverTrust];

        completionHandler(NSURLSessionAuthChallengeUseCredential,card);

    }
}

三、SDWebImage
1、重写sd_setImageWithURL方法，使用NSURLSession结合SDWebImage图片缓存机制，
在方法didReceiveChallenge，canAuthenticateAgainstProtectionSpace中进行证书验证

2、或是在SDWebImageDownloaderOperation.m 中的在方法didReceiveChallenge添加证书验证